n<br />\n利申 頂唔順fg果陣做港資日日返十幾個鍾 去左上海先發現原來工作唔應該佔據人生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:12:02.000Z","msg":"做到隻狗咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb91d38284d1d731419abc651914ae1c1dc164d","tid":761100,"uid":97551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"根本香港就係on撚鳩<br />\n<br />\n咁撚多人住大西北要出到去港島九龍返工<br />\n<br />\n搭巴士就塞車，搭地鐵就逼鳩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef585f6e34ad253e1c6edf4addbd6712218e6ba4","tid":761100,"uid":9812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"我以前<br />\n通勤 1.5hours<br />\n工時 11 hours<br />\n午飯 1 hour<br />\n睡眠 7hours<br />\n私人時間 3.5hours<br />\n<br />\n轉工後<br />\n通勤 30mins<br />\n工時 9 hours<br />\n午飯 1.5 hours<br />\n睡眠 7 hours<br />\n私人時間 6hours<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想曬命，而係想帶出有D人話後生仔住遠D無所謂捱下<br />\n但其實咁遠返工跟本就唔人道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dd7e009f6584564f9a222509e92806a1bd02b2","tid":761100,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acbfda1a127be21b86e4e2bf71b9fc05e9e27635","tid":761100,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"外國呢？"},{"pid":"e2b45d87cddcf18831df35f036176925685f1447","tid":761100,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"住天水圍 <br />\n返灣仔 女友住太古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 